So I mean, OPEC in oil and gas exists in significant part to have price control, to keep prices

01:02:38.540 --> 01:02:44.900
and profitability up, so if there's the danger of a kind of supply glut, they tell the members

01:02:44.900 --> 01:02:50.420
of OPEC, you know, close the taps for a bit to keep prices and therefore profits up.

