We're not talking about exponential price falls, we're talking about, you know, dramatic

01:03:37.940 --> 01:03:43.420
falls, but not as dramatic as something like Moore's Law, you know, the halving or the

01:03:43.420 --> 01:03:47.740
halving of costs every 18 months or the doubling of processing speed per dollar every 18 months.

